      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! It honestly breaks my heart a little to post this, but it\u2019s time for my pride and joy to find a new home. I have absolutely babied this beauty\u2014it\u2019s been tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and polished more often than I\u2019d like to admit! It looks and drives just like it did the day it left the showroom. You might find a tiny, tiny stone chip if you look with a magnifying glass, but to anyone else, she\u2019s absolutely flawless. Come on over, let\u2019s grab a coffee, and I\u2019ll show you why this is the one you\u2019ve been waiting for!",
